=== 孟加拉国 ===
在[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]，主要官員和國會議員均擁有「Honourable」敬稱，而總理及總統則分別擁有「The Honourable」和「His/Her Excellency」（[[閣下|閣下]]）的敬稱。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mopme.portal.gov.bd/sites/default/files/files/mopme.portal.gov.bd/page/1ba54097_b8c8_462d_bc48_d81f8d0e97c9/Scan0269.pdf |title=Ministry of Primary and Mass Education |publisher=''Government of The People's Republic of Bangladesh'' |date=2015-11-23 |accessdate=2016-04-22 |archive-date=2019-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522180614/https://mopme.portal.gov.bd/sites/default/files/files/mopme.portal.gov.bd/page/1ba54097_b8c8_462d_bc48_d81f8d0e97c9/Scan0269.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldleaders.columbia.edu/events/her-excellency-sheikh-hasina-prime-minister-government-bangladesh |title=Her Excellency Sheikh Hasina, Prime Minister of the Government of Bangladesh |publisher=''Columbia University World Leaders Forum'' |date=2015-09-25 |accessdate=2016-04-22 |archive-date=2019-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191222024352/https://worldleaders.columbia.edu/events/her-excellency-sheikh-hasina-prime-minister-government-bangladesh |dead-url=no }}</ref>

